text: The List of national parks in Albania includes the following: == National == * Butrint * Dajti Mountain * Divjaka-Karavasta * Lura * Llogara * Prespa * Thethi * Tomorri Mountain * Valbona Valley * Fir of Hotova-Dangëlli * Fir of Drenova * Shtam Pass * Zall-Gjoçaj * Shebenik-Jabllanica * Korab-Koritnik == Archaeological == * Amantia * Antigonea * Apollonia * Byllis * Hadrianopolis * Lissus * Oricum * Phoenice * Shkodra == Marine == * Karaburun-Sazan is sea water forming a 1 nautical mile radius from the shores of the Karaburun Peninsula, and Sazan Island.
